# Cerulean City
- Arrived Turn 2126
- West: Route 4 (one-way ledges prevent returning to Mt. Moon)
- North: Route 24 (Bridge is around X=20)
- South: Route 5 (Direct path blocked by Cut Tree at 19, 28)

[Points of Interest]
- Pokemon Center: (19, 17)
- Poke Mart: (25, 25)
- Bike Shop: (13, 25)
